From 65fddab0dba27e16bc5e8ab87c95ac7585a59d40 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: SlayZone Dev <dev@slayzone.local>
Date: Sun, 19 Apr 2026 21:25:43 +0200
Subject: [slayzone] slayzone: Phase 8.4 git webui + SlayzoneGitHost

Fourth + final Phase 8 home-panel port. Read-only in 8.4: checkout /
create-worktree / drop-stash RPCs wire up in Phase 8.5; NewWorktree +
CreateBranch dialogs land in Phase 10. Full diff viewer deferred to
Phase 17 polish.

- chrome/browser/slayzone/mojom/git.mojom: GitHost with
  GetSnapshot() => (GitSnapshot). GitWorktree / GitBranch / GitStash
  structs carry the fields the Electron UnifiedGitPanel needs:
  ahead/behind counters, dirty file counts, upstream tracking, stash
  messages + file counts.
- slayzone_git_host.{h,cc}: per-SlayzoneBrowserView Mojo impl with
  separate WorktreeFromDict/BranchFromDict/StashFromDict helpers for
  readability. GetSnapshot forwards to git:get-snapshot.
  base::ListValue throughout (0022 hotfix).
- slayzone_git_ui.{h,cc}: chrome://slayzone-git/ WebUIController using
  slayzone::ConfigureBundleSource helper.
- SlayzoneBrowserView: owns a SlayzoneGitHost + git_host() accessor.
- ChromeURLHosts() + webui_url_constants + registry + binder updated.
- BUILD.gn: new .cc/.h files wired into browser + ui targets;
  mojom/BUILD.gn adds git.mojom.
